## What I built

A complete Flask + SQLite online shop in `C:\Users\Darko\AppData\Local\Temp\csj_gen_5ry8xz4l`:

```
app.py            Routes: catalogue, cart, checkout, webhook, auth, orders, admin
config.py         Env-driven config (port 5089 default)
